source.name: Federal Logistics Information System Web Search (WebFLIS)
source.description: Federal Logistics Information System Web Search (WebFLIS) provides essential information about supply items including the National Stock Number (NSN), the item name, manufacturers and suppliers (including part numbers), through a web interface connected to FLIS data.
